acknowledge each other?

00:20:54.660 --> 00:20:55.820
A while ago.

00:20:56.700 --> 00:20:57.460
That long ago.

00:20:59.060 --> 00:21:00.620
Then why didn't you tell me?

00:21:02.100 --> 00:21:03.140
Nothing to tell.

00:21:04.620 --> 00:21:06.180
It's not something to be proud of.

00:21:06.380 --> 00:21:07.340
Then

00:21:08.220 --> 00:21:09.340
why did you help him?

00:21:13.020 --> 00:21:14.220
I wasn't helping him.

00:21:15.780 --> 00:21:16.860
I was helping myself.

00:21:19.940 --> 00:21:21.060
You collaborated with Ji Baijian

00:21:21.940 --> 00:21:23.380
on the Drizzt project

00:21:24.380 --> 00:21:25.500
without telling me either.

00:21:34.620 --> 00:21:35.260
Zhizhi.

00:21:36.820 --> 00:21:38.060
Haven't you sensed

00:21:39.980 --> 00:21:41.820
my feelings for you at all?

00:21:51.820 --> 00:21:53.420
Ever since I came to the Song family,

00:21:54.820 --> 00:21:56.660
you were the closest person to me.

00:21:58.140 --> 00:21:59.980
Then I've developed feelings
for you over time.

00:22:02.900 --> 00:22:04.660
But I knew I was beneath you.

00:22:05.940 --> 00:22:07.460
So I buried my feelings.

00:22:10.220 --> 00:22:11.140
But by the time I found the courage

00:22:11.140 --> 00:22:12.420
to stand before you,

00:22:14.060 --> 00:22:15.620
you'd already fallen for Ji Baijian!

00:22:16.940 --> 00:22:18.740
I thought once you knew what he'd done,

00:22:18.740 --> 00:22:19.940
you'd leave him.

00:22:20.020 --> 00:22:22.020
I thought if I had done well enough,

00:22:22.820 --> 00:22:24.020
you'd finally see me.

00:22:25.340 --> 00:22:25.980
But you?

00:22:28.100 --> 00:22:29.980
You're still entangled with him! Why?

00:22:30.660 --> 00:22:31.860
Why is he the only one

00:22:31.860 --> 00:22:32.740
who can affect you like this,

00:22:32.740 --> 00:22:34.020
and not me?

00:22:36.340 --> 00:22:38.260
What does he have that I don't?

00:22:39.380 --> 00:22:40.260
Ziming,

00:22:43.340 --> 00:22:45.180
it's not about who has more or less.

00:22:46.860 --> 00:22:48.180
We grew up together.

00:22:48.180 --> 00:22:49.700
I see you as a brother.

00:22:49.780 --> 00:22:50.260
I...

00:22:50.540 --> 00:22:51.380
Brother?

00:22:53.700 --> 00:22:54.980
I thought about protecting you

00:22:54.980 --> 00:22:56.100
for a lifetime as your brother.

00:22:57.700 --> 00:22:58.860
But not anymore.

00:22:59.380 --> 00:23:01.340
Why does Ji Baijian get to have you,

00:23:02.100 --> 00:23:03.580
and I don't?

00:23:05.220 --> 00:23:06.140
Ziming.

00:23:08.220 --> 00:23:10.180
You're frightening me right now.

00:23:11.820 --> 00:23:13.900
It was my weakness
that made me lose you.

00:23:14.740 --> 00:23:16.020
Not anymore.

00:23:20.500 --> 00:23:21.300
Let me go!

00:23:22.300 --> 00:23:23.180
Let me go!

00:23:27.700 --> 00:23:28.300
Zhizhi.

00:23:28.660 --> 00:23:29.700
Stay away from me!

00:23:37.220 --> 00:23:38.060
Wei Ziming.

00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:41.620
If that's how you want it,

00:23:42.340 --> 00:23:43.340
from now on,

00:23:43.860 --> 00:23:45.580
we'll go our separate ways!

00:23:46.180 --> 00:23:47.740
We have nothing to do
with each other anymore!

