♪The wind breaks the withered tree♪

00:24:28.600 --> 00:24:31.720
♪It's too weak to be propped up anymore♪

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:35.400
♪Scenes of the past replay
again and again♪

00:24:35.640 --> 00:24:38.920
♪Tired of being weak and helpless♪

00:24:39.320 --> 00:24:42.920
♪Honestly, I don't care♪

00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:46.280
♪Maybe it's a kind of gift♪

00:24:46.520 --> 00:24:49.680
♪Bitterness helps me comprehend♪

00:24:51.460 --> 00:24:52.820
Fine.

00:24:52.820 --> 00:24:55.460
