Ziming,

00:25:20.580 --> 00:25:22.620
I want to hold a party tomorrow.

00:25:23.060 --> 00:25:25.980
I'm going to let everyone know
that you're my son.

00:25:27.940 --> 00:25:28.780
Understood.

