Also,

00:25:33.620 --> 00:25:34.460
I'd like to

00:25:35.100 --> 00:25:36.580
talk with you
about some internal matters

00:25:36.860 --> 00:25:39.460
to prepare you
for joining the higher-ups.

00:25:42.020 --> 00:25:42.700
By the way,

00:25:43.940 --> 00:25:45.580
don't sign that second contract

00:25:47.900 --> 00:25:48.660
Song Zhizhi gave you.

00:25:50.380 --> 00:25:51.300
It's a trap.

00:25:55.860 --> 00:25:57.300
You're sharp, Ziming.

00:25:58.300 --> 00:25:59.140
Whatever you say.

