I want to return to Starlight Jewelry.

00:26:18.940 --> 00:26:20.140
Ms. Song, please take a look.

00:26:22.500 --> 00:26:24.140
I think the color gradient
on these two pieces

00:26:24.140 --> 00:26:26.220
