If I recall correctly,

00:27:05.300 --> 00:27:07.500
Starlight Jewelry is primarily
controlled by the Song family.

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:09.580
Since when do we
need a special commissioner

00:27:09.580 --> 00:27:10.740
