for the Drizzt project.

00:27:23.340 --> 00:27:24.500
Since the group is providing substantial

00:27:24.500 --> 00:27:25.860
funding and resources,

00:27:27.140 --> 00:27:29.220
it will supervise the daily management

00:27:29.940 --> 00:27:30.940
of Starlight Jewelry.

00:27:32.660 --> 00:27:34.300
Looking forward to working together.

