But Zhizhi,

00:28:29.740 --> 00:28:33.140
I told you I'd protect you.

00:28:33.900 --> 00:28:35.140
That promise still stands.

00:28:37.380 --> 00:28:38.780
If you're with me,

00:28:39.260 --> 00:28:40.980
Starlight Jewelry will always be yours.

00:28:46.260 --> 00:28:48.180
But if you're still acting
like you were yesterday,

00:28:49.180 --> 00:28:50.460
then I'll handle everything

00:28:51.500 --> 00:28:53.100
by the book from now on.

